MERCURIES LIFE said unconsolidated sales
in April rose 24.78% to NT$10,125,648,000 from NT$8,114,560,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2011           4/2010
Sales           10,125,648       8,114,560   
YOY%              24.78%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           41,159,375       44,934,232  
YOY%              -8.40% 
=================================================================
 